:Class App
‚ćĚ rhowars web API ‚ÄĒ Stark-based REST server
‚ćĚ
‚ćĚ   app‚Üź‚éēNEW rw.Web.App (StarkClass gameNS)
‚ćĚ   app.Start 8080

    :Field Private router
    :Field Private lastMatch
    :Field Private lastBotNames
    :Field Private game
    :Field Private defaultCfg
    :Field Private matches
    :Field Private nextMatchId
    :Field Private remotes
    :Field Private nextSlot

    ‚ąá Make args;StarkClass
      :Access Public
      :Implements Constructor
      (StarkClass game)‚Üźargs
      lastMatch‚Üź‚ć¨
      lastBotNames‚Üź‚ć¨
      matches‚Üź‚ć¨
      nextMatchId‚Üź1
      remotes‚Üź‚ć¨
      nextSlot‚Üź0
      router‚Üź‚éēNEW StarkClass
      router.Handlers‚Üź‚éēTHIS
      router.Info‚Üź(title: 'rhowars' ‚čĄ version: '0.1.0')
      defaultCfg‚ÜźSaveCfg
      game.BotLib.LoadAll
      '/api/match/list' router.Get 'ListMatches'
      '/api/match/{id}/history' router.Get 'GetMatchHistory'
      '/api/match/{id}/record' router.Get 'GetRecord'
      '/api/match/replay' router.Post 'ReplayRecord'
      '/api/match/history' router.Get 'GetHistory'
      '/api/match' router.Post 'StartMatch'
      '/api/match' router.Get 'GetMatch'
      '/api/bots' router.Get 'ListBots'
      '/api/bots' router.Post 'UploadBot'
      '/api/bots/{author}/{name}' router.Delete 'DeleteBot'
      '/api/config' router.Get 'GetConfig'
      '/api/config/reset' router.Post 'ResetConfig'
      '/api/match/{id}/end' router.Post 'EndMatch'
      '/api/match/{id}/situation' router.Get 'GetSituation'
      '/api/remote/list' router.Get 'ListRemotes'
      '/api/remote/{slot}/{token}/state' router.Get 'GetRemoteState'
      '/api/remote/{slot}/{token}/action' router.Post 'PostRemoteAction'
    ‚ąá

